Tags: tag are index given to the entries (tag name, slug, color, icon)
Categories: Categories are the way to group the entries (category name, slug, color, icon)
Entries: Entries are the actual content (entry name, description, date, time, category, tags, history)
History: History is the way to track the changes made to the entries (entry, change type, change date, change time, change description)

Tasks: Task is trackable list of the entries with additional details
Calendar: Entries tagged with date:time for calender entry

